{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775902789762,"sessionID":"ses_283f50cecffeSn1ZLPg1jFwh0T","part":{"id":"prt_d7c0e02f5001tDIQ5oXAHkrJNc","messageID":"msg_d7c0df1ec0019KYCrjr7G5uDZI","sessionID":"ses_283f50cecffeSn1ZLPg1jFwh0T","type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"toolu_functions.bash:8","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"wc -l /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/python-sdk/design.md && head -50 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/python-sdk/design.md","description":"Verify design.md was written"},"output":"804 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/python-sdk/design.md\n# AR-027 Design: AgentCube Python SDK — CodeInterpreterClient\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-027  \n**Module:** `sdk-python`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M (Medium)\n\nThe AgentCube Python SDK provides a client library (`agentcube-sdk`) for creating Code Interpreter sessions via the Workload Manager (control plane) and executing code/files via the Router (data plane), plus invoking AgentRuntime workloads through the Router.\n\nThis implementation integrates with:\n- **Workload Manager API**: Control plane for session lifecycle management\n- **Router API**: Data plane for code execution and file operations\n- **Agent Runtime API**: For agent workload invocation\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         User Application (Python)                            │\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────┐                 │\n│  │ CodeInterpreterClient   │    │  AgentRuntimeClient     │                 │\n│  │ ┌───────────────────┐   │    │ ┌───────────────────┐   │                 │\n│  │ │ Context Manager   │   │    │ │ Context Manager   │   │                 │\n│  │ │ Lifecycle Mgmt    │   │    │ │ Lifecycle Mgmt    │   │                 │\n│  │ └───────────────────┘   │    │ └───────────────────┘   │                 │\n│  └───────────┬─────────────┘    └───────────┬─────────────┘                 │\n│              │                              │                                │\n└──────────────┼──────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────┘\n               │                              │\n               ▼                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         SDK Internal Layer                                   │\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │   ControlPlaneClient        │    │       Data Plane Clients            │  │\n│  │  ┌───────────────────────┐  │    │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │ Session Management    │  │    │  │ CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient│  │  │\n│  │  │ · create_session()    │──┘    │  │ · execute_command()           │  │  │\n│  │  │ · delete_session()    │       │  │ · run_code()                  │  │  │\n│  │  └───────────────────────┘       │  │ · write_file()                │  │  │\n│  │  HTTP Session (requests)         │  │ · upload_file()               │  │  │\n│  │  · Connection pooling            │  │ · download_file()             │  │  │\n│  │  · Auth: Bearer token            │  │ · list_files()                │  │  │\n","metadata":{"output":"804 /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/python-sdk/design.md\n# AR-027 Design: AgentCube Python SDK — CodeInterpreterClient\n\n## Overview\n\n**AR ID:** AR-027  \n**Module:** `sdk-python`  \n**Language:** Python  \n**Size:** M (Medium)\n\nThe AgentCube Python SDK provides a client library (`agentcube-sdk`) for creating Code Interpreter sessions via the Workload Manager (control plane) and executing code/files via the Router (data plane), plus invoking AgentRuntime workloads through the Router.\n\nThis implementation integrates with:\n- **Workload Manager API**: Control plane for session lifecycle management\n- **Router API**: Data plane for code execution and file operations\n- **Agent Runtime API**: For agent workload invocation\n\n---\n\n## Architecture\n\n### High-Level Design\n\n```\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         User Application (Python)                            │\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────┐                 │\n│  │ CodeInterpreterClient   │    │  AgentRuntimeClient     │                 │\n│  │ ┌───────────────────┐   │    │ ┌───────────────────┐   │                 │\n│  │ │ Context Manager   │   │    │ │ Context Manager   │   │                 │\n│  │ │ Lifecycle Mgmt    │   │    │ │ Lifecycle Mgmt    │   │                 │\n│  │ └───────────────────┘   │    │ └───────────────────┘   │                 │\n│  └───────────┬─────────────┘    └───────────┬─────────────┘                 │\n│              │                              │                                │\n└──────────────┼──────────────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────┘\n               │                              │\n               ▼                              ▼\n┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐\n│                         SDK Internal Layer                                   │\n│                                                                              │\n│  ┌─────────────────────────────┐    ┌─────────────────────────────────────┐  │\n│  │   ControlPlaneClient        │    │       Data Plane Clients            │  │\n│  │  ┌───────────────────────┐  │    │  ┌───────────────────────────────┐  │  │\n│  │  │ Session Management    │  │    │  │ CodeInterpreterDataPlaneClient│  │  │\n│  │  │ · create_session()    │──┘    │  │ · execute_command()           │  │  │\n│  │  │ · delete_session()    │       │  │ · run_code()                  │  │  │\n│  │  └───────────────────────┘       │  │ · write_file()                │  │  │\n│  │  HTTP Session (requests)         │  │ · upload_file()               │  │  │\n│  │  · Connection pooling            │  │ · download_file()             │  │  │\n│  │  · Auth: Bearer token            │  │ · list_files()                │  │  │\n","exit":0,"description":"Verify design.md was written","truncated":false},"title":"Verify design.md was written","time":{"start":1775902789741,"end":1775902789760}}}}
